"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fierce spat\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 433}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 463}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2023 World Athletics Championships\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite being an underdog, Scotsman Kerr beat the2020 Tokyo gold medallistin the 1500m with a seasonal best of 3:29.38 to Ingebrigtsen's 3:29.65.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 592, \"end\": 597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.5778561143213076, \"rank\": 0.7304731679722768, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an underdog\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"Scotsman Kerr\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 578}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1500m\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"3:29.38\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen's 3:29.65\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the defeat did not sit well with the 23-year-old from Rogaland who attributed sickness to his defeat while claiming that if he was fully fit, he could beat Kerr \\\"blindfolded\\\".\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 864, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 743, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rogaland\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.6454156842279e-13, \"text\": \"Rogaland\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rogaland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rogaland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the defeat\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 699}, {\"ngram\": \"sickness\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 775}, {\"ngram\": \"his defeat\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 789}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 849}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He claimed: \\\"I would have beaten him in that race blindfolded,\\\" adding: \\\"But it's good that people run better than they have done before.\\\"\", \"from\": 865, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that race\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kerr, however, later hit back: \\\"I am like, 'You have won so many races, you ran fantastic all season that you are just on this - you must be surrounded by so many yes-men that you do not realise that you have weaknesses'.\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1226, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"so many races\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1075}, {\"ngram\": \"so many yes-men\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"weaknesses\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I think that was part of his downfall.\\\"\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1272, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"his downfall\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He went on: \\\"If he does not realize that he's got some real major weaknesses, then he will not win the 1500 meter gold medal next year.\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some real major weaknesses\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1500 meter gold medal\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And you know, I am OK with that ...\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I would love for him to be listening to this.\\\"\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans of the sport have questioned whether the bad blood between the two runners is real or just heat of the moment, but Kerr is insistent that the two are \\\"not friends\\\".\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Fans\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1501, \"to\": 1510}, {\"ngram\": \"the bad blood\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"the two runners\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"real or just heat\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1660}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a recent interview with The Times, the 26-year-old said: \\\"People are asking, 'Is it real?'\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1690, \"end\": 1699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times\", \"score\": 0.9999992407318286, \"rank\": 7.592683542721085e-07, \"text\": \"The Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Times\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a recent interview\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1684}, {\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"or whatever.\\\"\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"or whatever\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1768}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He added: \\\"I do not speak to him.\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1807, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not speak to the people I do not want to speak to because we are not friends.\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1836}, {\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's not our relationship.\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our relationship\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's fine.\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not care.\\\"\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Team GB star also hopes to bury the hatchet once and for all when an Olympic medal is on the line come Tuesday evening.\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 2076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Team GB star\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"the hatchet\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2000}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2039}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2054}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking afterSunday's semi-final,in which Jakob bested Kerr by 0.08 seconds with a time of 3:32.38, he said: \\\"Fans should expect the most competitive 1500 meter the sport has seen in a long time.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2121, \"end\": 2126, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.5032722273777325e-31, \"text\": \"Jakob\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jakob_Ingebrigtsen\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kerr\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2138}, {\"ngram\": \"0.08 seconds\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2166}, {\"ngram\": \"3:32.38\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"Fans\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2193}, {\"ngram\": \"the most competitive 1500 meter\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2239}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2249}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is been a lot of talking words over the last few years.\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2294},